These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, daffodil
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, march, october
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, ship, trike
 1. the person driving the roller is the german##1
 2. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the italian and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the colombian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Flower      | amaryllis    | daffodil   | poppy           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Birthday           | november | march   | october      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Transport         | roller     | ship | trike |

