.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue, grey
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
House: townhouse, tower, cottage
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, zinnia
 1. the cottage house is the british##1
 2. the cottage house is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person who likes coral##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
10. the cottage house is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Color   | grey       | light-blue      | coral         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| House           | townhouse        | cottage      | tower         |
| Flower         | iris | begonia  | zinnia |

