There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
City: berlin, nizza, prague
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who growsdaisy is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person who growslily is the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the indian and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the indian is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage          | water      | mirinda      | fanta      |
