The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, sports
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, malaysian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 2. the person who likes amber is the malaysian##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes amber##2
 6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person driving the bus is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person who likes green is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the bike##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Color      | amber | green           | red      |
| Sport         | cycling       | cricket         | rowing       |
| Transport           | bus    | van | bike |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | sports         | disaster      |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | country        | jazz          |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | egyptian       | dutch         |
| Pet           | mouse       | ferret         | lizard        |

