 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the american##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
11. the person driving the subway is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Food         | cauliflower     | nectarine     | pomegranate  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Color           | yellow        | apricot | brown     |
| Flower         | amaryllis    | poppy | lily   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

