.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, july
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, bellflower
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, russian, german
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, septembersy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the german##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the polish##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the russian##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the german and the person who growsbellflower##2
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the person watching septembersy movies is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday      | september      | june      | july       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| Flower         | bellflower    | sunflower     | daisy     |
| Nationality           | russian    | polish | german   |
| Movie-Genre   | septembersy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

