6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

