.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, photography, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, comedy
3 different games are played: bridge, snooker, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person drinking tea and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
9. the person watching crime movies is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Hobby          | video-games   | camping   | photography  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | crime     | comedy  |
| Game           | mah-jongg     | bridge        | snooker |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 